{"tid":963483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地非洲豬瘟失控　港鬆懈恐淪陷","createTime":"2018-12-31T15:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T16:45:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"711b9431ce20bc0b25f4dcb2f6f5cce740187a48","tid":963483,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:05:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181231/20580490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F20580490&d=6yZlErWEhdfD04ocpivlSp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=056fe138\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F20580490&h=faf24cbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181231/20580490</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月31日 <br />\n<br />\n內地非洲豬瘟失控　港鬆懈恐淪陷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181231/large/a1003a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181231%2Flarge%2Fa1003a.gif&h=712cedad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地非洲豬瘟疫情失控，自2018年8月3日遼寧瀋陽爆發今年首宗非洲豬瘟後，不足五個月席捲全國23省市，北京、上海先後淪陷，廣東近日亦失守，珠海、順德、廣州及惠州分別爆發疫情，累計撲殺生豬逾63萬隻，20個供港豬場暫停豬隻輸港。非洲豬瘟源頭眾說紛紜，中方研究人員暗示病毒源自俄羅斯東西伯利亞地區，但俄方否認，反指瘟疫或來自歐盟及中東。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181231/large/a1003b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181231%2Flarge%2Fa1003b.gif&h=ffa3ea4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181231/large/a1003c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181231%2Flarge%2Fa1003c.gif&h=3309ead0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：豬商北上發展　本地苛政殺農業<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n無論內地的非洲豬瘟源頭由哪裏出現，本港每日平均約有4,000隻內地活豬進口，防範疫症傳入最為關鍵。但養豬業界批評現行機制在口岸、屠房以至運輸層面上存在五大漏洞，最離譜是上水、荃灣兩個屠房連一個消毒池也沒有，運豬車出入毋須全車消毒，車身亦非密封式，隨時令非洲豬瘟殺入本港。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n豬商北上發展　本地苛政殺農業<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n傳入途徑眾說紛紜<br />\n<br />\n豬商北上發展　本地苛政殺農業<br />\n傳入途徑眾說紛紜<br />\n非洲豬瘟Q＆A<br />\n如何分辨問題豬肉<br />\n社會專題：新丁擲數千萬　電腦管理養港豬"},{"pid":"3aaa50f3128a435fe9fc36768683f7de49f7a59d","tid":963483,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T16:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c66375e6c72f3e7b7673849c2196e2a7af634ac","tid":963483,"uid":18912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T16:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UuzQ4h1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuzQ4h1.gif&h=8096669b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}